This game is an original, independent implementation. It is based on the rules
of "Scoundrel", a solo card game designed by Zach Gage & Kurt Bieg (2011).
Game rules and mechanics are not covered by copyright; this project contains no
text, artwork, or code from the original rules document. "Scoundrel" and
"Balatro" are the property of their respective creators. This is an unofficial,
non-commercial fan adaptation and is not affiliated with or endorsed by them.

The MIT license above applies only to this project's own source code.
